{"word":"G989 - βλάσφημος - blásphēmos - blas'-fay-mos - Blasphemer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βλάσφημος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>blásphēmos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>blas'-fay-mos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Blasphemer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தூஷணம், தூஷிக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"speaking evil, slanderous, reproachful, railing, abusive"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G984 - βλάπτω - bláptō - blap'-to/984\">G984</a> and <a href=\"#/G5345 - φήμη - phḗmē - fay'-may/5345\">G5345</a>; <i>scurrilous</i>, that is, <i>calumnious</i> (against man), or (specifically) <i>impious</i> (against God): - blasphemer (-mous), railing."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G987 - βλασφημέω - blasphēméō - blas-fay-meh'-o/987\">G987</a>, <a href=\"#/G988 - βλασφημία - blasphēmía - blas-fay-me'-ah/988\">G988</a>, <a href=\"#/G989 - βλάσφημος - blásphēmos - blas'-fay-mos/989\">G989</a>"}]}